---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 xl:px-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium mb-8">RIDI TERMS OF SERVICE</h1>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Last Updated: 2025-04-29</p>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-4">
            By using Ridi ("the App"), you agree to these legally binding terms.
            If you disagree, you must immediately stop using the App.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4">2. Route Generation Service</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-4">
            Ridi provides route suggestions based on OpenStreetMap (OSM) data
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2">
            <li>
              We make reasonable efforts to avoid suggesting private or
              prohibited roads
            </li>
            <li>
              All routes are suggestions only - actual road conditions may
              differ
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4">3. Important Disclaimers</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">a. No Warranty of Accuracy:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Route quality depends entirely on OSM data accuracy</li>
            <li>We cannot guarantee routes will be:</li>
            <ul class="list-circle pl-6 text-lg space-y-1">
              <li>Safe or legal for riding</li>
              <li>Free from obstructions or hazards</li>
              <li>Suitable for your skill level or bike type</li>
            </ul>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">b. No Liability:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2">
            <li>You use all routes at your own risk</li>
            <li>We expressly disclaim responsibility for:</li>
            <ul class="list-circle pl-6 text-lg space-y-1">
              <li>Any accidents, injuries or damages</li>
              <li>Route inaccuracies or omissions</li>
              <li>Unexpected road conditions (construction, closures, etc.)</li>
              <li>Trespassing on private property</li>
            </ul>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4">4. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-4">You agree to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2">
            <li>Independently verify all routes before riding</li>
            <li>Obey all traffic laws and respect private property</li>
            <li>Wear proper safety gear and ride within your abilities</li>
            <li>Not hold Ridi liable for any consequences of route use</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">
            General Exclusion of Liability
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-4">
            To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>
              Ridi disclaims all liability for any damages, losses, or injuries
              arising from use of the app or its generated routes
            </li>
            <li>
              This includes but is not limited to: direct, indirect, incidental,
              special, consequential or punitive damages
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">User Assumption of All Risks</h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-4">You expressly agree:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2">
            <li>All route usage is at your sole and absolute risk</li>
            <li>
              You assume complete responsibility for verifying route safety and
              legality
            </li>
            <li>
              Ridi provides routes "as is" without any representations or
              warranties
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4">6. Data and Privacy</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2">
            <li>Your use of the App is subject to our Privacy Policy</li>
            <li>We store your route history to improve the service</li>
            <li>
              We use Sentry for crash reporting to improve app stability and
              identify issues
            </li>
            <li>
              We use PostHog for analytics to understand app usage patterns and
              improve user experience
            </li>
            <li>
              You may request data deletion at <a
                href="mailto:info@ridi.bike"
                class="text-[#f75835] hover:underline">info@ridi.bike</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4">7. General Provisions</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2">
            <li>We may modify these terms with notice</li>
            <li>These terms are governed by Latvian law</li>
            <li>Any disputes must be resolved in Latvian</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4">8. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-lg">
            For questions: <a
              href="mailto:info@ridi.bike"
              class="text-[#f75835] hover:underline">info@ridi.bike</a
            >
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
